IMAPStore gmail-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User sdysch94@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass mail/gmail"
AuthMechs LOGIN
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.local/share/mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/gmail/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim
Flatten .

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns INBOX "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Drafts" "[Gmail]/Trash"
Create Both
Sync All
Expunge Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 50
ExpireUnread no
